data.description: This is a real find, single family home on an oversized lot with NO HOA!This 3 bedroom home features a nice open floorplan with high ceilings, laminated wood floors.Kitchen has wood cabinets, granite countertops  & SS appliances.  the garage is being used as additional living space.The back yard is a outdoor lovers dream. The yard is fully shaded by the large trees, It's fenced in and there is plenty of  space for a pool. The shed will stay with the property. The roof is only 3 years old and the A/C  was done within the last 5 years all ducts cleaned and a U/V light installed.
